  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Granted by @UUID[Compendium.pf2e-misc.our-items.Item.rW8ujIJiylHFpz7u]{Warlord's Strategic Stance} and @UUID[Compendium.pf2e-misc.our-items.Item.aqXheGYb1BFNH3YI]{Defensive Position}</p><p>You order your allies to stay close and cover each other.</p><p><strong>Effect</strong> Affected allies gain a +1 circumstance bonus to AC and reflex saving throws. If the ally is wielding a shield or can cast the Shield cantrip, they can raise their shield or cast Shield as a free action once during their turn. If they're wielding a weapon with the parry trait, they can parry instead.</p>",
